snippet.title: Crime Boss: Rockay City: Dragon's Gold Cup Expansion Pack Trailer [ESRB M 17+]
snippet.description: Travis Baker (played by Michael Madsen), a distrustful and spiteful gangster, joins forces with his ultimate rival, Dollar Dragon (played by Danny Trejo) in the first Expansion Pack for Crime Boss: Rockay City. Available NOW on Epic Games Store, PS5 and Xbox Series X|S.
